  "title": "Sales Consultant in Maid Agency",
  "description": "<p>Established maid Agency required experience Sale Consultant. Working location either in Hougang Green shopping Mall/Bukit timah Shopping Center or Sin Ming Road. Required KAH or CEI certification. Basic salary $3000 and above with high commission per sale.</p>\n<p>Established in 2012, EP One Manpower Pte Ltd is a one of the leading maid agencies in Singapore. Our 3 branch offices are located at Bukit Timah, Hougang and Sin Ming Road. We take pride in providing excellent value added services to our clients; both the Employers and the Migrant Domestic Worker(MDW), Our sales consultant and supporting staff work as a close team to achieve our goals.</p>\n<p>Currently we have 2 sales consultant vacancies openings in our organization. If you have the confidence to do sales and able to work independently, yet being a team player, we welcome you to apply with us. Basic salary starts from $3200 above depending on experience level. High commission per sale. Website:- <a href=\"https://epone.netmaid.com.sg/\">https://epone.netmaid.com.sg</a></p>\n<p>Job requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>KAH or CEI certified.</li>\n  <li>Self motivated, sale oriented and able to handle customers independently. Provide after sales support</li>\n  <li>6 day work week</li>\n  <li>Manage enquiries</li>\n  <li>Handle documents and applications</li>\n  <li>Conduct and arrange interviews for clients</li>\n  <li>Condusive working enviroment</li>\n  <li>No previous experience in maid agency will be considered.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>please email your resume to Mr Yeo at <a href=\"mailto:tongpohyeo53@gmail.com\">tongpohyeo53@gmail.com</a> or WhatsApp to 96188275.</p>",
